## MVP in one paragraph

**Step 1:** **One button** (best UI, no redirect) — valid JWT = **instant** (no button, no PEGIN); else one tap → Face ID. Account once (username + passkey + DID). **Not** DIG-led. See [user-facing-ux-principles.md](docs/02-product/user-facing-ux-principles.md). **Step 2:** **Vault** (chia-wallet-sdk / Rigidity Rue) so DID is **recoverable** on **multiple devices** — **seed phrase** (recovery only) + **passkey** (login + re-bind new device). DIG application layer, email guardian, Chia Signer → after MVP.

## External repos (prototype)

- [chia-wallet-sdk](https://github.com/xch-dev/chia-wallet-sdk) — DID, `VaultInfo`, JWT bridge
- [rue](https://github.com/xch-dev/rue) — vault (Step 2)
- [sage](https://github.com/xch-dev/sage) — Tauri shell
- [dig-l2-storage](https://github.com/DIG-Network/dig-l2-storage) — post-MVP

